def roof_fix(new, old):
    return all(patch == ' ' for patch, tile in zip(new, old) if tile in '\/')

def roof_fix(f, r):
    return all(x == ' ' or y == '_' for x,y in zip(f, r))

def roof_fix(f,r):
    return all(b == ' ' for a, b in zip(r, f) if a in '\//')

def roof_fix(f,r):
    return all(b not in r'\/' or a == ' ' for a, b in zip(f, r))

def roof_fix(f,r):
    return all(new==' ' for old, new in zip(r,f) if old in "\/")

def roof_fix(f,r):
    return all((b in'\/')<=(a==' ')for a,b in zip(f,r))

def roof_fix(f,r):

def roof_fix(f,r):
